PROCEDURE: IN A VERY CLEAN UBATOL SLOWLY AND CAREFULLY ADD SULPHURIC ACID TO DEMIN WATER. **ALWAYS DO IT IN THIS ORDER - NEVER ADD WATR TO THE ACID** DO NOT MAKE IN MAIN MIXING VESSEL, DUE TO HEAT EVOLVED, MAY BURST TANK. WHEN ALL ADDED PUT LID ON UBATOL TO MINIMISE EVAPORATION WHICH WILL OCCUR DUE TO HEAT OF THE REACTION. PUT UBATOLS WHICH SHOULD BE CAREFULLY LABELLED TO ONE SIDE AND ALLOW TO COOL TO ROOM TEMPERATURE THEN STIR IN MAIN POLY MIXING VESSEL FOR 10 MINS. SAMPLE TO LAB FOR TESTING
HSE: CORROSIVE. CAUSES SERIOUS BURNS TO HUMAN TISSUE. NEVER ADD WATER TO THIS PRODUCT
